version_description: Those versions are wrong, the do not even sound right
Hello all. For this tab, the 2017 Broadway version, performed by Brendon Urie, is used. The first version of this tab is the original version in C Major, whereas this one is in the key of B.
The strumming pattern is quite hard to write down, but if you think in 'one and a two and a three' etc you should figure it out.

I have made corrections to the timing, kept chords in the original key signature, and added labels to the sections. There are also corrections to the lyrics, diagrams for chords, and instructions on how to read this tab.
